an style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提起馬賽用番真名司馬賽兒，Laura即刻落地有骨，寸爆馬賽話：「件事係破咗我底線，唔係話攞把刀㓤完人，改咗名就當冇傷過人。」</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec102c5e1669e64790e21634807a2dd54b756d9c","tid":681241,"uid":125079,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"睇心靈雞湯？好呀，睇多啲以形補形<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bee4d749ef45b673d01834facb3220cb8695ae4","tid":681241,"uid":55519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"當年呢單新聞好juicy"},{"pid":"b9587a8b2721b9b2fc3eb02787bb694e19a9b65f","tid":681241,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"942bb55e2068e9e13d7c307b44a554c7028d2e68","tid":681241,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec102c5e1669e64790e21634807a2dd54b756d9c","tid":681241,"uid":125079,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"睇心靈雞湯？好呀，睇多啲以形補形<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaeef07d37bece31f0a6a4f4e6fb51c55c534b2","tid":681241,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018