d05e2a4b338f6ffda2f0770","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"三問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"四問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"tory burch有出沐浴露？？"},{"pid":"e2a67d8e9ed8bff4f4f7c45d474b78eb79294546","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑似 馬賽 私信 曝光　自爆 失處給 汪子琦：每天當我性奴 忽然1周 1011期</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咩事呀，每天當我性奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年底馬賽被踢爆撬富婆好友 Laura牆腳，與內地女製片人汪子琦撻着，在上海街頭上演啜啜騷，搞到滿城風雨。今年 7月她更被人公開穿情趣內衣跳艷舞的短片，外表斯文的她，原來內裏 open。<br />\n事後馬賽被大台明雪暗捧，過冷河唔夠半年就繼續有工開，她亦貫徹低調博洗底，微博再沒更新。直至日前她上載兩幀佛堂照，藉信仰重新開始，不過似乎冇咁易。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">那年周一，有人在她的微博，上載疑似馬賽與大台某花旦密友的私信，她除自爆失處過程，更牽涉到與疑似吳卓羲及 TB汪的牀上性事，內容震撼。</span></span>私信被公開後，翌日一早，馬賽即把私信原先的愛犬頭像 icon換走。周四凌晨，馬賽在微博留言，表示事件是誹謗與造謠，已交由警方處理，看來這事件真是耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n2008年的港姐季軍馬賽，出道後緋聞不斷，一直以「純純兔」形象面對公眾。直到去年底，她與汪子琦同遊上海，態度親暱，其後汪女友富婆 Laura現身踢爆馬賽先以朋友身份接近她們，再埋身搶走汪。事後馬賽雖然在大台節目中否認一切，但形象已直插谷底，被大台雪藏，不過兩星期後即獲樂易玲極速解凍。<br />\n事件並未就此平息，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">那年 7月，馬賽跳艷舞的片段及露點照片曝光，她開記招承認自己是照片中人，並指是為了討好汪子琦才拍下有關影片。汪隨後接受訪問，指是馬賽主動穿上情趣內衣跳艷舞勾引自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span></span>馬賽再次遭大台暫停所有工作，同樣地事隔不足半年即獲解凍，更火速安排她拍攝新劇《東坡家事》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後台撐腰馬賽先後被爆同性戀及拍艷舞片，形象直插谷底，但仍遭大台放生兼繼續有劇拍，冇後台撐腰真係令人難以置信。 <br />\n<br />\n打頭陣<br />\n疑似馬賽私信曝光　自爆失處給汪子琦：每天當我性奴<br />\n<br />\n私信對話露骨<br />\n已大半年絕跡微博的馬賽，日前更新微博即惹禍上身，有人把疑似是她的私信， post於她的微博內公諸於世。私信中可見馬賽的愛犬頭像以及官方認證碼，而內容涉及與疑似汪子琦及疑似吳卓羲性愛內容。"},{"pid":"092bd06c7fa8e7784e261d9ce785dc0364cdd8c7","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b557c3df45d1ceb7a7e2f913b49f4f651e6ce36c","tid":681241,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfef90958c74739dd2d31cdda910ba5303ccad69","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a9b27be8dba6435c98f82a8baa3445a9263c86","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"三問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"四問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"tory burch有出沐浴露？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0abb8b7f909b50417dc160e42252a64a6df3e3f","tid":681241,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092bd06c7fa8e7784e261d9ce785dc0364cdd8c7","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b557c3df45d1ceb7a7e2f913b49f4f651e6ce36c","tid":681241,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfef90958c74739dd2d31cdda910ba5303ccad69","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"四問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"tory burch有出沐浴露？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係第一次聽<br />\n好想聞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6001155e5a5055202de0b46fd22c20746e8a30","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0abb8b7f909b50417dc160e42252a64a6df3e3f","tid":681241,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092bd06c7fa8e7784e261d9ce785dc0364cdd8c7","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b557c3df45d1ceb7a7e2f913b49f4f651e6ce36c","tid":681241,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"tory burch有出沐浴露？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係第一次聽<br />\n好想聞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"我都想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea09ac371b867a87b58e18f4fac060937d3e1c4","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"記者林佑珊／綜合報導<br />\n香港女星馬賽（司馬賽）2008年獲得香港小姐季軍，不久就被電視台簽下出道，因長相清純還有「迷你桂綸鎂」的封號。而她2013年才被爆出介入富婆Laura和大陸知名女製作人汪子琦的戀情，從此形象慘跌一度被冷凍，好不容易「復出」最近又被人翻出疑似她身穿情趣內衣大跳艷舞的不雅影片，再度引起一陣譁然。<br />\n<br />\n據香港《壹週刊》報導，影片中疑似馬賽的女子，身穿知名拍賣網上一款約人民幣9.9元至22元（約台幣48至107元）上下的情趣內衣，搭配40至50年代當紅美國女歌手女歌手Doris Day所唱得《Perhaps Perhaps Perhaps》，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在鏡頭前搔首弄姿大跳艷舞，被細繩勒住的私處，和在珍珠串間若隱若現的乳頭十分引人遐想</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，影片和截圖一曝光就在網路被人瘋狂轉載。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更引人注意的是，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這位疑似馬賽的短髮女子除了不斷擺動身體、扭晃水蛇腰，還一度將雙手探至大腿中間，接著由下往上撫摸鼠蹊部，畫面極盡挑逗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>而這支影片曝光後，有網友認為應該只是長得很像的人，也有人認為女主角就是本尊，看法非常不一。"},{"pid":"216adb54d6f845c81dba2bfdac22e7495cdb9bc5","tid":681241,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fecea118ccfcb9d545d0067651c3bf0c93f1f3","tid":681241,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"TB點破人地處？🤔"},{"pid":"92f47f80f9406c2f36e08dfc9bd2234f45a8c0bf","tid":681241,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"兩個TB係到獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226d50f0b13021e9806b69dcca05e3fa570f002d","tid":681241,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"頂你CG動畫整到好似I社既3D H動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ad6d056dbb83bcb58123c446d1a197b3a85c9c","tid":681241,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fecea118ccfcb9d545d0067651c3bf0c93f1f3","tid":681241,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"TB點破人地處？🤔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"玩假鳩"},{"pid":"0b9a2f1796fc323340399501e6c799a4a2a19af6","tid":681241,"uid":73048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d